commentText: Removes given config option from the configuration.__@param configOption config option to remove_@param <T> Type of the config option_@return true is config has been removed, false otherwise
codeText: public <T> boolean removeConfig(ConfigOption<T> configOption){_		synchronized (this.confData){_			_			Object oldValue = this.confData.remove(configOption.key())__			if (oldValue == null){_				for (String deprecatedKey : configOption.deprecatedKeys()){_					oldValue = this.confData.remove(deprecatedKey)__					if (oldValue != null){_						LOG.warn("Config uses deprecated configuration key '{}' instead of proper key '{}'",_							deprecatedKey, configOption.key())__						return true__					}_				}_				return false__			}_			return true__		}_	}
